Author: pinapelz
Name: Malmstone Calculator
Description:
Calculate how much more PVP you have to play before reaching a certain series level in the current PVP Series
Use /pmalm to open the main window
Punchline: A PVP Series Malmstone Level Calculator

Author: pinapelz
Name: DiscordToXIV
Description:
XIVToDiscord? Why not DiscordToXIV. This plugin allows you to bring Discord messages into FFXIV and send text from FFXIV to Discord!
**Requires BetterDiscord**
